  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[STORY]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is Vampire Castle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A traveler who came here not knowing that</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vampire A smiled.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oh, look at all that delicious food we've got.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now, how can I scare you, my dear?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I can't wait to see the looks of terror and despair on their faces.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169250/extras/43474d764517e65855af5f4226242ca3.poster.avif?t=1771567021\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169250/extras/43474d764517e65855af5f4226242ca3.webm?t=1771567021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169250/extras/43474d764517e65855af5f4226242ca3.mp4?t=1771567021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Overview].</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a survival escape game from vampires.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hide in the shadows to avoid being found by the vampires.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the items you need to escape in the mansion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find objects where you can hide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Listen carefully because the closer the enemy gets, the louder the footsteps become.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you hear the sound, hide in the shadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you make it back alive in one piece?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[STORY]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is Vampire Castle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A traveler who came here not knowing that</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vampire A smiled.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oh, look at all that delicious food we've got.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now, how can I scare you, my dear?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I can't wait to see the looks of terror and despair on their faces.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169250/extras/43474d764517e65855af5f4226242ca3.poster.avif?t=1771567021\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169250/extras/43474d764517e65855af5f4226242ca3.webm?t=1771567021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169250/extras/43474d764517e65855af5f4226242ca3.mp4?t=1771567021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Overview].</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a survival escape game from vampires.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hide in the shadows to avoid being found by the vampires.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the items you need to escape in the mansion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find objects where you can hide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Listen carefully because the closer the enemy gets, the louder the footsteps become.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you hear the sound, hide in the shadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you make it back alive in one piece?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
